title: Yong zheng ming zhang Shao Lin men (1977)

sources.title: Yong zheng ming zhang Shao Lin men (1977)
sources.description: Two sword-wielding sisters seek revenge against the villains who murdered their family. But these are no ordinary villains — they’re wizards with giant, elasticized tongues who use black magic to control... kung fu gorillas! Watch on RetroFlix:  https://retroflix.org/yong-zheng-ming-zhang-shao-lin-men-1977/
